Thank you, Dr. Ashish, for bringing up
that very wonderful point,

00:20:17.520 --> 00:20:21.760
a very relevant point about
the level of reactions that we all may have.

00:20:21.760 --> 00:20:25.200
And it is for each of us to,
just look inside us, look around us

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:29.600
to see where we find just giving reactions
more than needed.

00:20:29.600 --> 00:20:33.200
Like you explained with the example
of the cat and the tiger responses

00:20:33.200 --> 00:20:35.520
to a similar situation
or a different situation,

00:20:35.520 --> 00:20:36.960
how they need to be.

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:42.000
But this is something that we are seeing
a lot around us on social media

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:44.000
and different platforms.

