Fabulous. That's such a great point,
Monika,

00:20:58.240 --> 00:21:02.800
if we think of our evolution,

00:21:02.800 --> 00:21:07.040
but we don't have to go back
to the aquatic stage.

00:21:07.040 --> 00:21:09.920
Just about 100 years ago,
just about 50 years ago,

00:21:09.920 --> 00:21:11.360
there was no social media,

00:21:11.360 --> 00:21:14.960
television and media did not play
