00:26:28.300 --> 00:26:38.700
Shri Mataji: Today we are going to understand
the center of Agnya,

00:26:38.700 --> 00:26:48.220
Agnya chakra which is placed
on the crossing of the optic chiasma.

00:26:48.220 --> 00:26:56.700
The nerves that supply the eyes
go backwards in the opposite direction,

00:26:56.700 --> 00:27:06.620
and wherever they cross,
this subtle center is situated.

00:27:06.620 --> 00:27:11.660
It has a continuous connection
with the other center

00:27:11.660 --> 00:27:16.500
through the medulla oblongata.

00:27:20.860 --> 00:27:37.020
This center has got two petals
and this subtle center on one side

00:27:37.020 --> 00:27:48.860
acts through the eyes and at the back
of the head where you have some protrusion.

00:27:48.860 --> 00:27:53.340
This is the physical side of the center.

00:27:53.340 --> 00:28:03.642
The people who talk of the third eye,
this is the third eye.

00:28:11.640 --> 00:28:15.000
Keep your eyes closed.

00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:19.880
First of all, please put your right hand
on your heart.

00:28:19.880 --> 00:28:23.880
All the time the left hand is towards Me.

00:28:23.880 --> 00:28:34.200
Now, here you have to say in your heart,
with all sincerity, Mother, am I the Spirit?

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:36.840
Ask the question three times
in your heart.

00:28:36.840 --> 00:28:40.950
This is a very fundamental question.

00:28:58.040 --> 00:29:06.200
Now bring the right hand
on to the left hand side of your stomach,

00:29:06.200 --> 00:29:10.120
in the upper part.

00:29:10.120 --> 00:29:11.480
Here press it.

00:29:11.480 --> 00:29:19.960
Now this is the center of your mastery,
your guidance, your guru Tattva, as they say.

00:29:19.960 --> 00:29:24.360
So ask a question,
Mother, am I my own master?

00:29:24.360 --> 00:29:26.680
This is the question to be asked
three times.

00:29:26.680 --> 00:29:32.511
Mother, am I my own master?

00:29:44.280 --> 00:29:52.440
Now bring your right hand down below
in the lower part of the abdomen.

00:29:52.440 --> 00:30:00.120
Now this is the center from which
all the Divine work is done,

00:30:00.120 --> 00:30:02.920
all the pure work is done.

00:30:02.920 --> 00:30:08.040
So to ask six times,
because this center has got six petals,

00:30:08.040 --> 00:30:13.720
Mother, please give me pure knowledge.

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:16.920
Six times you just ask.

00:30:16.920 --> 00:30:22.151
As a result of this asking
the Kundalini starts getting awakened.

00:30:33.031 --> 00:30:37.800
Now to help the Kundalini to rise
you have to cooperate with Her.

00:30:37.800 --> 00:30:41.960
So please put your right hand
on the left hand side

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:51.160
in the upper part of your abdomen
and press it on the stomach.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:56.840
Now here you have to say
with full confidence,

00:30:56.840 --> 00:31:03.560
to help the Kundalini to rise,
Mother, I am my own master.

00:31:03.560 --> 00:31:05.800
This you have to say ten times.

00:31:05.800 --> 00:31:08.840
These are the ten commandments
which you have to say,

00:31:08.840 --> 00:31:13.575
that Mother, I am my own master.

00:31:49.960 --> 00:31:56.360
Now, ten times with full confidence.

00:31:57.320 --> 00:32:06.440
Now please raise your right hand
to your heart.

00:32:06.440 --> 00:32:13.320
Now here you have to say,
again with full confidence,

00:32:13.320 --> 00:32:15.720
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:32:15.720 --> 00:32:18.120
This is the truth, you are the Spirit.

00:32:18.120 --> 00:32:23.560
But you have to say with full confidence,
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:32:24.520 --> 00:32:28.316
This you have to say twelve times.

00:32:55.800 --> 00:33:02.920
Now one has to know
that God Almighty is the ocean of love.

00:33:02.920 --> 00:33:07.800
But above all He is the ocean
of forgiveness.

00:33:07.800 --> 00:33:09.640
So He forgives.

00:33:09.640 --> 00:33:12.280
Whatever wrong you do He forgives.

00:33:12.280 --> 00:33:19.960
So don't feel guilty
and put your right hand across

00:33:19.960 --> 00:33:28.440
on the left hand side in the corner
which is made by your neck and your shoulder.

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:32.600
Now here you have to say
again with full confidence,

00:33:32.600 --> 00:33:36.360
sixteen times, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:33:36.360 --> 00:33:39.640
Please say it, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:33:39.640 --> 00:33:43.080
Sixteen times.

00:33:43.080 --> 00:33:46.443
I am not guilty at all.

00:33:46.443 --> 00:33:54.579
Please say it.

00:34:24.600 --> 00:34:34.120
Now raise your hand across on your forehead
and it's a very important center.

00:34:34.120 --> 00:34:44.920
Here you have to say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:34:44.920 --> 00:34:47.160
Please say it from your heart.

00:34:47.160 --> 00:34:49.240
How many times is not the point.

00:34:49.240 --> 00:34:53.640
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:34:53.640 --> 00:34:57.320
Now some would say
that it's very difficult to forgive.

00:34:57.320 --> 00:35:03.240
But it's a myth
that we do not forgive or we forgive.

00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:06.120
We do not do anything
in both the cases.

00:35:06.120 --> 00:35:10.120
But if we don't forgive
then we play into wrong hands.

00:35:10.120 --> 00:35:17.108
So please say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:35:24.520 --> 00:35:31.720
Now please take your hand on the back agnya,
the same center, on the back side of your head

00:35:31.720 --> 00:35:36.760
and allow your head to rest on it
and push it back a little bit.

00:35:37.560 --> 00:35:44.120
Now here you have to say
for your satisfaction,

00:35:44.120 --> 00:35:50.600
because you always feel guilty,
that, O Divine, if I have done anything wrong,

00:35:50.600 --> 00:35:53.910
please forgive me.

00:35:59.720 --> 00:36:08.120
Please forgive me, from your heart.

00:36:08.120 --> 00:36:14.680
Stretch your hand fully
and put your center of your palm

00:36:14.680 --> 00:36:23.480
on top of the fontanel bone area,
which was a very soft bone in your childhood.

00:36:23.480 --> 00:36:24.680
Press it hard.

00:36:24.680 --> 00:36:28.200
Press hard your scalp.

00:36:28.200 --> 00:36:34.440
Now you have to move it seven times
saying one thing, which you have to ask for,

00:36:34.440 --> 00:36:39.720
Mother, please give us My Self-realization,
because I cannot force on you.

00:36:39.720 --> 00:36:42.440
So you have to ask for it.

00:36:42.440 --> 00:36:51.000
Seven times press it hard
and move it seven times very hard.

00:36:51.000 --> 00:36:55.294
Slowly saying that.
